<div class="main" id="animation-element">
    <!-- Animation content -->
    <% if (!animationPlayed) { %>
        <style>
            .main-body {
                position: absolute;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                background-color: #FFFFFF;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                color: #000000;
                font-size: 3rem;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                z-index: -1;
            }

            .main {
                background-color: #1E1E1E;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                animation: slideUpWindow 2s ease-in-out forwards;
                z-index: 2000;
            }

            @keyframes slideUpWindow {
                0% {
                    top: 0;
                }

                100% {
                    top: -100%;
                }
            }

            .main {
                animation: slideUpWindow 2s ease-in-out 3s forwards;
                /* Added a 3-second delay */
            }


            .animation-container {
                font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
                font-weight: bold;
                color: #FFFFFF;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                white-space: nowrap;
                margin: 5%;
            }

            .text-container {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                position: relative;
            }

            .letter {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(50px);
                display: inline-block;
                animation: slideUp 0.5s ease-in-out forwards;
                animation-delay: calc(0.2s * var(--animation-order));
                /* Animation delay based on order */
            }

            .special-i {
                position: relative;
                align-items: baseline;
                display: inline-block;
                vertical-align: bottom;
                transform-origin: bottom;
                animation-name: slideUp, morph;
                animation-timing-function: ease-in-out, ease-out;
                animation-delay: 0s, 2s;
                animation-duration: 0.5s, 0.5s;
                animation-fill-mode: forwards;
            }

            .dot {
                position: absolute;
                top: -2em;
                /* Start position above */
                left: 50%;
                transform: translateX(-50%);
                width: 20px;
                height: 20px;
                background-color: transparent;
                border-radius: 50%;
                opacity: 0;
                /* Initially hidden */
                animation: dropDot 0.5s ease-in-out forwards;
                animation-delay: 2.1s;
                /* Start the drop after 'I' appears */
            }

            @keyframes slideUp {
                0% {
                    opacity: 0;
                    transform: translateY(50px);
                }

                100% {
                    opacity: 1;
                    transform: translateY(0);
                }
            }

            @keyframes morph {
                0% {
                    color: #FFFFFF;
                    transform: scaleY(1);
                }

                100% {
                    color: #FDA700;
                    transform: scaleY(0.8);
                }
            }

            @keyframes dropDot {
                0% {
                    opacity: 0;
                    top: -2em;
                }

                100% {
                    opacity: 1;
                    top: -0.2em;
                    background-color: #FDA700;
                }
            }

            .letter,
            .special-i {
                font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 12rem);
                /* Responsive font size */
            }

            @media (max-width: 768px) {
                .animation-container {
                    margin: 10%;
                }

                .letter,
                .special-i {
                    font-size: clamp(4rem, 15vw, 18rem);
                }

                .dot {
                    width: 30px;
                    height: 30px;
                }

                /* Adjust dot size for better visibility */
            }


            .navbar {
                top: 5%;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: space-between;
                align-items: center;
                /* background-color: #000; */
                color: #000000;
                padding: 10px 20px;
            }

            .navbar div {
                margin: 0 10px;
            }

            .logo {
                font-size: 24px;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

            .search {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .menu {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .menu div {
                margin: 0 15px;
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .icons {
                font-size: 16px;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .icon {
                margin-left: 15px;
                width: 24px;
                height: 24px;
                background-color: #FFF;
                /* White icons */
                mask: url(icon-placeholder.png) center/cover no-repeat;
            }
        </style>
        <div class="main">
            <div class="animation-container">
                <div class="text-container">
                    <span class="letter" style="--animation-order:1;">B</span>
                    <span class="letter" style="--animation-order:2;">r</span>
                    <span class="letter" style="--animation-order:3;">a</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-container">
                    <span class="letter special-i" id="specialI" style="--animation-order:4;">I</span>
                    <div class="dot" id="dot"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-container">
                    <span class="letter" style="--animation-order:5;">n</span>
                    <span class="letter" style="--animation-order:6;">b</span>
                    <span class="letter" style="--animation-order:7;">e</span>
                    <span class="letter" style="--animation-order:8;">a</span>
                    <span class="letter" style="--animation-order:9;">c</span>
                    <span class="letter" style="--animation-order:10;">o</span>
                    <span class="letter" style="--animation-order:11;">n</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
</div>

                                </pattern>

                                </pattern>
                                <image id="image0_100_138" width="980" height="980"
                                    xlink:href="data:image/png;base64," />
                            </defs>
                        </svg>
                        <div style="right: 10%;">

                  <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email ID">

                  <button class="login-btn" type="submit">Login</button>

        </div>
    </div>
    <% } %>
</div>
